The cabinet approved bill making easier government issue commemorative coin , Finance Ministry official said .
The bill , must still approved parliament , would take effect April 1988 .
It would allow government issue 1,000 , 5,000 10,000 yen coin without special legislation , although higher-valued coin would still need special law , official said .
At present issue coin 500 yen le .
